---
// Nosotros.astro
---

<section id="nosotros" class="py-24 px-6 bg-white relative overflow-hidden font-montserrat">
  <div class="absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-96 h-96 bg-[#ECF9FF] rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-50 -z-10"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-16">
    
    <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 relative">
      <div class="relative z-10 rounded-[40px] lg:rounded-[60px] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border-5 border-white">
        <img 
          src="/images/equipo-sima.jpg" 
          alt="Equipo Sima24" 
          class="w-full h-[400px] lg:h-[500px] object-cover"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-2 lg:right-6 z-20 bg-[#0056b3] text-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl flex items-center gap-4 animate-bounce-slow">
        <span class="text-4xl font-black italic">15+</span>
        <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider leading-tight">
          Años de<br/>Compromiso
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="absolute -top-8 -left-4 z-0 text-[#00D0B4] opacity-40">
        <svg width="80" height="80" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M19 13h-6v6h-2v-6H5v-2h6V5h2v6h6v2z"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 space-y-8 text-center lg:text-left">
      <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 bg-blue-50 text-[#0056b3] rounded-full text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">
        Sobre Nosotros
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-[#003366] leading-tight">
        Pasión por la <span class="text-[#0056b3]">Vida</span> y la Excelencia Médica
      </h2>
      
      <p class="text-gray-600 font-medium text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Sima24 nace con el propósito de transformar la respuesta médica en el occidente del país. No solo somos ambulancias; somos un equipo humano dedicado a protegerte en los momentos más críticos.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 pt-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-[#00D0B4]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#00D0B4]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="font-bold text-[#003366]">Seguridad Garantizada</span>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-[#0056b3]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#0056b3]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="font-bold text-[#003366]">Atención Inmediata</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-4">
        <p class="text-gray-500 italic border-l-4 border-[#00D0B4] pl-4">
          "Nuestra misión es acortar distancias cuando la salud no puede esperar."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes bounce-slow {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
  }
  .animate-bounce-slow {
    animation: bounce-slow 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
</style>